terra (0.1.8); urgency=low

  * Experimental slide effect.
  * Start fullscreen option.
  * Advanced multi monitor features.
  * Change font size with <Control>+mouse scroll
  * Option to change exit signal behavior


terra (0.1.7); urgency=low

  * Now Terra using 'libkeybinder3.0' instead of pure python and python-xlib based keybinder library.
  * All XLib related crash and slow opening issues fixed.
  * Hide on lose focus feature re-enabled.
  * Select-by-word charachters added.
  * Change font size with <Control>+/-
  * TRANSLATORS file added.
  * "Translate this application" button and "terraterminal.org" link added.
  * Spanish, French, Catalan, Catalan (Valencian) translations added.

  -- Özcan ESEN <ozcanesen@gmail.com> 

terra (0.1.6); urgency=low

  * Switch between terminals with keyboard shortcuts.
  * Clickable links
  * Automatically hide resizer bar when fullscreen
  * Clear assigned keyboard shortcut with double click
  * Hide tab bar option
  * Hide tab bar when fullscreen option
  * Shortcut key to show/hide scrollbars 
  * Added button for restore default key settings
  * Prompt on quit option
  * Ctrl+D or exit signal closes terminal
  * If there is no terminal left tab closes automatically
  * If there is no tab left Terra closes automatically
  * i18n support, now you can translate and use Terra in your language
  * Turkish translation.

  -- Özcan ESEN <ozcanesen@gmail.com> 

terra (0.1.5); urgency=low

  * Multi Monitor support
  * Remember tab name option
  * Scrollback options
  * Copy/Paste shortcuts fixed on context menu 
  * Transparency problems fixed

  -- Özcan ESEN <ozcanesen@gmail.com> 

terra (0.1.4); urgency=low

  * First public release with main features.

  -- Özcan ESEN <ozcanesen@gmail.com> 